&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate effectively with cross-functional teams, including testers, and product managers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Foster a collaborative and inclusive work environment where ideas are shared and valued.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
